{"tid":1041994,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"國內泊車法？中港車打斜硬攝　阻路「頂住晒」","createTime":"2019-03-01T08:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T01:01:17.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b411090db29914e5fc22a44dc383ab68a4a03b03","tid":1041994,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>國內泊車法？中港車打斜硬攝 阻路「頂住晒」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NzULp7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NzULp7&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=6d74ee9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2NzULp7</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190301/photo/bkn-20190301163112165-0301_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190301164619\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190301%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190301163112165-0301_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190301164619&h=e8c99d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大地任我泊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n揸車容易泊車難，遇上窄位可以點泊？有中港車就使出特別的泊車技巧，打斜插入兩車中間，凸出的「屁股」擋着半條行車線，被網民怒斥︰「離晒譜」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民於周四（28日）在Facebook群組「巴打絲打Facebook Club」上載照片，只見灣仔莊士敦道近郵政局對開，當時路邊泊滿車輛。有掛着中港牌的七人車疑見空位不足，遂打斜45度角，硬插入僅餘的空位中。惟部分車身凸出，阻擋行車線。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民批評該中港車：「邊有人泊車衰成咁」、「正自私X，報警拖車啦」、「大陸泊車係咁，但呢度係香港」、「頂X住晒」。"},{"pid":"dbcc567cbe84200a20d3cacf5af84deb5dc05628","tid":1041994,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"中港牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d96315a08be85e2501c17a23455df488b20088","tid":1041994,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:59:14.000Z","msg":"呢隻唔係叫中港牌<br />\n係100%大陸FV狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e4c3b939223349297b9b3305e824090216659b","tid":1041994,"uid":66242,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"藍牌係正宗中国人<br />\n嚟香港作客"},{"pid":"db3ae3ddddfa64fa0e97a5c0c5ed4ba5bd926eb7","tid":1041994,"uid":91638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39e4c3b939223349297b9b3305e824090216659b","tid":1041994,"uid":66242,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"藍牌係正宗中国人<br />\n嚟香港作客"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲仲衰撚過黑色中港牌個啲大陸司機"},{"pid":"03ca901b8a392eab80989be008e798d198ed6964","tid":1041994,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:26:43.000Z","msg":"有時係避車處打斜泊可以泊多一兩部車"},{"pid":"9276fbbc8f78024f72d65b2d7f4557d0d9978558","tid":1041994,"uid":221586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"國內？"},{"pid":"fb7d9524ad5313785f7e2f8e41401fc42c1cb307","tid":1041994,"uid":74910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"泊得靚唔阻人就利曼起步泊法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泊得衰搞著路面車就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e96dc49963a6b5913f7fe3d11bab8c5f63eccd","tid":1041994,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T01:01:17.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攬炒"}]}